  "title": "General Insurance (GI) Sales Executive",
  "description": "<p>Are you a <strong>driven and customer-focused individual</strong> looking for a rewarding career in the insurance industry? Join our dynamic team as a <strong>General Insurance Sales Executive</strong> and help clients secure their future with the right protection!</p><h3><strong>🔹 Job Responsibilities:</strong></h3><p>✅ <strong>Provide Insurance Solutions</strong> – Advise clients on general insurance products (e.g., motor, home, travel, health, and commercial insurance).<br />✅ <strong>Assess Client Needs</strong> – Understand customer requirements and recommend suitable coverage options.<br />✅ <strong>Sales & Business Development</strong> – Build and maintain relationships with new and existing clients.<br />✅ <strong>Claims Assistance</strong> – Guide clients through the claims process and ensure smooth settlements.<br />✅ <strong>Stay Updated</strong> – Keep up with industry trends, new insurance policies, and regulatory changes.</p><h3><strong>🔹 What We Offer:</strong></h3><p>✨ <strong>Attractive commissions & incentives</strong><br />✨ <strong>Flexible working hours</strong> – Work-life balance and control over your schedule.<br />✨ <strong>Training & support</strong> – Guidance from company and ongoing industry training.<br />✨ <strong>Career growth opportunities</strong> – Build a long-term career with leadership potential.</p><p>🎯 <strong>Join us and make a difference in people’s lives while building a successful career!</strong></p>",
